---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
import CTA from '@/components/CTA.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Miles Sowden | Insurance Executive, Growth and Transformation"
  description="Twenty years leading Australian insurers through growth and transformation. $1 billion in premium, 700 people, five major financial institutions."
  ogImage="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-48 pb-32 max-md:pt-32 max-md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <div class="md:flex md:items-start md:gap-16">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h1 class="font-display text-[3.5rem] max-lg:text-5xl max-md:text-[2.5rem] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary mb-10">
            Twenty years leading Australian insurers through growth and transformation
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mb-10">
            I diagnose systemic problems, design phased strategies, build the teams and capabilities to execute, and leave organisations stronger than I found them. I have led businesses with more than $1 billion in premium and teams of 700 across five major financial institutions. I treat data, technology, and AI as strategic assets that reshape how insurers compete.
          </p>
          <!-- Headshot: mobile only, between paragraph and buttons -->
          <div class="md:hidden mb-10 w-[200px]">
            <img
              src="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
              alt="Miles Sowden"
              width="200"
              height="230"
              class="w-full rounded-lg"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap max-md:flex-col">
            <CTA href="/contact" external={false}>
              Contact
            </CTA>
            <CTA href="#work-and-impact" variant="secondary" external={false}>
              Work and impact
            </CTA>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Headshot: desktop only, right column -->
        <div class="hidden md:block w-[280px] flex-shrink-0">
          <img
            src="/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg"
            alt="Miles Sowden"
            width="280"
            height="322"
            class="w-full rounded-lg"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How I lead -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        How I lead
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Four defining patterns across twenty years and five roles.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-x-16 gap-y-12 mt-16">
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Systemic diagnosis and phased transformation</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Every role starts the same way. Understand the root causes, not the symptoms. Design a strategy that sequences for impact. Build capability in layers. Combined ratio from 101.5% to 89.2% at CBA. From 105% to 98% at Suncorp. Digital availability from less than 5% to 60% at SCI.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Customer outcomes as the organising principle</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Strategy, pricing, operations, technology, and culture designed backward from customer outcomes. Not as a statement of values. As an operating discipline. NPS from +15 to +45 at CBA. From +25 to +44 at Westpac. CANSTAR Outstanding Value five consecutive years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Building capability that outlasts the leader</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">The test of leadership is not what happens while you are there. It is what happens after you leave. Designed a 10-person executive team at CBA that stayed in place after divestment. Built succession at SCI that delivered sustained results after departure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-text-accent pt-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-3">Designing the CEO operating model</h3>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">The CEO role has three value streams: strategic direction, external connection, and internal execution discipline. No single person excels at all three simultaneously. The CEOs who perform design their office and their leadership team to cover all three.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Work and impact -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20" id="work-and-impact">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <h2 class="font-display text-[2.5rem] max-md:text-[2rem] leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.02em] text-text-primary">
        Work and impact
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary mt-6">
        Two decades of outcomes across major Australian financial institutions, including through the Royal Commission, record catastrophe seasons, mergers and regulatory reform.
      </p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-8 mt-16">
        <a href="/work/sci" class="block p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card no-underline hover:bg-bg-card/80 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Strata Community Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">General Manager, Data and Technology Solutions</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Built a direct insurer within a broker-dominated business. Sequenced operations, digital, then AI. Cleared a 30,000-task backlog, reduced underwriting cycle time by 19%, deployed agentic AI at 97% accuracy. Digital availability from less than 5% to 60%.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/work/cba" class="block p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card no-underline hover:bg-bg-card/80 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Commonwealth Bank</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">General Manager, General Insurance</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Led a $1 billion insurer through the Royal Commission, pandemic, regulatory reform, and divestment. Combined ratio from 101.5% to 89.2%. Motor profitable for the first time in 15 months. Digital sales from 20% to 70%. NPS from +15 to +45.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/work/hollard" class="block p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card no-underline hover:bg-bg-card/80 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Hollard Insurance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Chief Revenue Officer</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Signed the ASIC Pricing Promise Review attestation at a second insurer. Entered the Cyclone Reinsurance Pool. Nine-month tenure confirmed the importance of alignment between executive and board on transformation appetite.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/work/suncorp" class="block p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card no-underline hover:bg-bg-card/80 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Suncorp and Promina</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Product Manager Roles</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Delivered the first underwriting profit in intermediated personal lines after four consecutive years of losses. Combined ratio from 105% to 98% through pricing, underwriting rules, product consolidation, claims effectiveness, and distribution rationalisation.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/work/westpac" class="block p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card no-underline hover:bg-bg-card/80 transition-colors">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Westpac Banking Corporation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Senior Management Roles</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Grew the insurance portfolio from $115m to $200m. Originated the strategic recommendation for a single alliance partner. Ran a six-month competitive process. Allianz selected. NPS from +25 to +44. Staff engagement from 66% to 92%.</p>
        </a>
        <div class="p-10 max-md:p-8 bg-bg-card">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl leading-[1.3] text-text-primary mb-2">Agentic Engineering</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary/70 mb-4">Independent projects</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Building AI-powered tools and automation outside of corporate roles. This site was designed and deployed using agentic workflows, Claude Code and modern web infrastructure as a practical demonstration of how AI changes the way work gets done.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Closing -->
  <section class="py-32 max-md:py-20 bg-bg-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-12 max-lg:px-8 max-md:px-6">
      <p class="text-xl max-md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-white/90">
        If you lead, chair, or advise a medium-sized Australian general insurer where data, technology, and AI are treated as strategic assets, I would welcome a conversation.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 text-base font-medium no-underline rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 bg-text-accent text-white border-[1.5px] border-text-accent hover:bg-[#B36F4F] hover:border-[#B36F4F]">
          Contact
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Person JSON-LD -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Miles Sowden",
    "jobTitle": "Insurance Executive",
    "description": "Twenty years leading Australian insurers through turnarounds, regulatory reform, and digital transformation. Strategy, teams and culture that deliver lasting performance.",
    "url": "https://madebymiles.ai",
    "image": "https://madebymiles.ai/images/miles-sowden-headshot.jpeg",
    "sameAs": [
      "https://www.linkedin.com/in/milessowden"
    ],
    "knowsAbout": [
      "General Insurance",
      "Business Transformation",
      "Strategic Leadership",
      "Artificial Intelligence",
      "Data Strategy",
      "Corporate Governance"
    ],
    "hasCredential": [
      {
        "@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential",
        "credentialCategory": "Professional Certification",
        "name": "Graduate, Australian Institute of Company Directors (GAICD)"
      },
      {
        "@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential",
        "credentialCategory": "Executive Education",
        "name": "Massachusetts Institute of Technology (MIT)"
      },
      {
        "@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential",
        "credentialCategory": "Postgraduate",
        "name": "Graduate Diploma of Applied Finance (GDipAppFin)"
      },
      {
        "@type": "EducationalOccupationalCredential",
        "credentialCategory": "Undergraduate",
        "name": "Bachelor of Business (BBus)"
      }
    ],
    "hasOccupation": [
      {
        "@type": "Occupation",
        "name": "General Manager, Data and Technology Solutions",
        "occupationLocation": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Australia" },
        "description": "Strata Community Insurance"
      },
      {
        "@type": "Occupation",
        "name": "General Manager, General Insurance",
        "occupationLocation": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Australia" },
        "description": "Commonwealth Bank"
      },
      {
        "@type": "Occupation",
        "name": "Chief Revenue Officer",
        "occupationLocation": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Australia" },
        "description": "Hollard Insurance"
      },
      {
        "@type": "Occupation",
        "name": "Product Manager Roles",
        "occupationLocation": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Australia" },
        "description": "Suncorp and Promina"
      },
      {
        "@type": "Occupation",
        "name": "Senior Management Roles",
        "occupationLocation": { "@type": "Country", "name": "Australia" },
        "description": "Westpac Banking Corporation"
      }
    ]
  })} />
</Base>
